OL,3,CMinefield-clearing robot to be
OL,4,Ctrialled for British Army front lines
OL,6,FA robot mine sweeper that has been
OL,7,Fdeveloped in Newcastle is being
OL,8,Ftrialled by the British Army to
OL,9,Feventually clear explosives on the
OL,10,Ffront lines.
OL,12,FIt is hoped the device, called WEEVIL,
OL,13,Fwill replace current mine-clearing
OL,14,Fmethods that require a three-person
OL,15,Fcrew to operate in hazardous areas.
OL,17,FThe new technology can be operated via
OL,18,Fremote control by a single person from
OL,19,Fseveral miles away and is fitted with
OL,20,Fa mine plough to clear a safe path.
