OL,3,CMinefield-clearing robot to be
OL,4,Ctrialled for British Army front lines
OL,6,FThe prototype was successfully tested
OL,7,Fin Newcastle on a surrogate minefield,
OL,8,Fand the technology is now being passed
OL,9,Fto the British Army for further
OL,10,Fdevelopment.
OL,12,FLuke Pollard, Minister for the armed
OL,13,Fforces, said: "It won't be a moment
OL,14,Ftoo soon when we no longer have to
OL,15,Fsend our people directly into harm's
OL,16,Fway to clear minefields.
