OL,6,F"This kit could tackle the deadly
OL,7,Fthreat of mines in the most
OL,8,Fchallenging environments, while being
OL,9,Fremotely operated by our soldiers
OL,10,Fseveral miles away."
OL,12,FDSTL military adviser Major Andrew
OL,13,FMaggs said: "WEEVIL is the perfect
OL,14,Fcombination of tried and tested
OL,15,Ftechnology and modern advancements.
